                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00"/>
                           <desc> Fol. 2va-b: ʾƎsäggǝd lä-mäläkotǝkä zä-fäṭärkä ṣǝlmätä… “I worship Thy Godhead that created the darkness…” (cp. ChRep no. 335).</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is possibly written in the main hand. Each daily reading is separated by a chain of red and black dots.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2"> <locus target="#3ra">Fols. 3ra</locus>-vb: Hymns.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is possibly written in the main hand and contains the following hymns: ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl bä-kǝlʾe Maryam wäladitä [ʾamlak] ʾǝmmu lä-ʾǝgziʾǝnä ʾiyäsus Krǝstos kähali… “O my Lady, Holy Two-fold Virgin Mary, Godbearing, Mother of our Lord Jesus Christ the Almighty…” (cp. ChRep no. 373); Sälam läki Maryam ʾǝmmä nädd wä-ʾǝmmä wahǝd ʾǝmmä nǝṣuḥ wä-ʾǝmmä mäśiḥ… “Salutation to you, Mary, Mother of the flame and Mother of the unique One, Mother of the pure One and Mother of the Messiah”.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3"> <locus target="#3vb">Fols. 3vb</locus>l.16-4ra: Calendaric note. <q xml:lang="gez"> Fol. 3vb ls. 16-21: በስ[መ፡] አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ባሕረ፡ ሐሳብ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ ዓለም፡ ከተፈጠረ፡ ዘመን፡ ቢቈጠር፡ ፯ሺህ፡ ከ፭፻ከ፭፡ ዘመን፡ ሆነ፡ ይሏል፡ ዓቢይ፡ ቀመር፡ ለመወቅ፡ …</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is written in Gǝʿǝz and Amharic and indicates the computation of the time since the creation of the world. The second part on fol. 4ra has been erased.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The scribe reduced the size of his handwriting to accommodate the end of the line: fols. 6va, 18vb, 26rb.&#xD;
- The scribe used compressed script: fols. 2rb.&#xD;
