- Omitted letters or words inserted interlineally in black ink: e.g., fols. 6ra, 9vb, 45va, 80va, 88ra.&#xD;
- Erasure: fol. 37va.&#xD;
- Corrections written over erasures in the main hand: fols. 12rb, 18rb, 28rb, 54va.&#xD;
- Corrections written over erasure in a secondary hand in red ink: fol. 29ra.&#xD;
- Spaces for rubrication left unfilled (for the name of the donor?): fols. 7rb, 8rb, 9rb, 10va, 12vb etc.&#xD;
- Scribbles: fols. 1r, 18r, 53v, 97v.&#xD;
- Crude notes in pencil: fols. 53v, 97r.</item>
